<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f6f9fc; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .logo { color: #1a56db; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; text-decoration: none; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding-top: 20px; }
    .alert-box { background-color: #fffaf0; border-left: 4px solid #ed8936; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #1a56db; color: white !important; font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">Proteccio CMS - Admin Alert</div>
    
    <h2 style="color: #111827; margin-top: 0;">New Rights Request Received</h2>
    
    <p>A new <strong>{{requestType}}</strong> has been submitted and requires review.</p>
    
    <div class="alert-box">
      <p><strong>Case Number:</strong> {{caseNumber}}</p>
      <p><strong>Requester:</strong> {{requesterName}}</p>
      <p><strong>Regulation:</strong> {{regulation}}</p>
      <p><strong>Priority:</strong> {{priority}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>Please log in to the admin dashboard to assign a reviewer and begin the verification process.</p>

    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">View Request</a>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Proteccio Data Privacy. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
